{"tid":984861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦涉向法官掟銀仔 女保安：一粒黃豆都可掟死人","createTime":"2019-01-17T06:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T13:05:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"68120d3479d093c21234310c8e9174c7c17ebd0d","tid":984861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcUL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7f2058c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&h=d8cfe54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月17日 <br />\n<br />\n婦涉向法官掟銀仔<br />\n女保安：一粒黃豆都可掟死人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190117/large/17la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190117%2Flarge%2F17la8p11.jpg&h=b708b6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女被告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】患抑鬱的醫管局前女工，自言不滿高院法官未有公平處理其民事索償案，涉向上訴庭三名法官「掟銀仔」洩憤，銀仔沒擊中任何人，但有女保安員報稱受驚。女工昨否認普通襲擊罪受審，強調當時「向冇人嘅地方掟，目的係唔想掟到人」；女保安則謂聽到「喀喀聲」即感生命有威脅，更反問女工：「一粒黃豆都可以掟死人，你有冇聽過？」案件下周三裁決。<br />\n<br />\n女被告賴容（50歲）沒律師代表，昨甫開庭即向裁判官香淑嫻訴說案發因由，堅稱只向無人的走廊擲幣，揚言「可以睇帶」。香官表示法庭只有錄音系統、並沒錄影功能，賴疑惑地問：「點解嘅？裝假狗呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒預計到有人如此大膽<br />\n<br />\n涉事女保安朱肖雲供稱，案發去年6月20日獲指派到4號法庭觀察被告舉動，坐在法官席前的她突然聽到「喀喀聲」，即望向聲音來源，發現有數個毫子硬幣。朱自言：「好詫異，點解會咁㗎？掟到我點算呢？」並稱當時「有驚」，沒預計到有人如此大膽，在莊嚴法庭內掟東西。香官問朱在哪一階段感害怕，她答：「睇到個銀仔時。」被告即謂：「你話你望到個銀仔開始驚，你望到個銀仔係一毫子，反而應該唔驚！」朱不同意，更反問：「一粒黃豆都可以掟死人，你有冇聽過？」被告面露詫異謂：「黃豆真係未聽過，嚇親我。」朱及後澄清聞聲已驚。<br />\n<br />\n高級保安員事後向上訴庭法官請示如何處理，法官只禁止被告再次入庭，未有下令報警，但副保安主任李興亞報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n被告稱只想投訴民事法官要求她索取醫療報告，後來她花費3.7萬元取得報告，法官卻指不呈交也可，「法官唔尊重法庭，叫市民點尊重？佢可以咁做，我哋市民都可以咁做。」案件表證成立，被告辯稱感萬般委屈，甚至打算自殺，當日原想找法官申冤，但投訴不果反遭保安包圍和監視，有感煩擾和嬲怒才擲硬幣，「我其實想去馬道立嗰度，但唔識去」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1527/18<br />\n■記者楊思雅  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n社交網「大量張學友飛」引黃牛黨現身　內地男遭南亞賊搶14萬元<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n司機涉危駕被捕　聖保羅校巴倒車撞死保母"},{"pid":"a01d04e6b2f0b2ed9d21e38886ace1c59632e8c7","tid":984861,"uid":35430,"like":206,"dislike":1,"score":205,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"當女人胸部都可以襲警罪成<br />\n黃豆掟得死人又有幾奇？"},{"pid":"c92e89f3f4239468a2bcfb5279f8441cf4acf6e4","tid":984861,"uid":120892,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"掟毫子咁小家㗎<br />\n而家最少都掟100蚊紙啦"},{"pid":"08c6fdfc71ebdf43a43e1c1a5db2404c0c639ea6","tid":984861,"uid":74361,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-sv6XvoDlPw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-sv6XvoDlPw&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcUL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=265d986d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-sv6XvoDlPw</a><br />\n送粒黃豆比你"},{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},{"pid":"87ed77c60927bf2ffc385e466d4a2282d2a22e83","tid":984861,"uid":39381,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"用黃豆槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c86016177603a096266597ce63fcbed3cea83a","tid":984861,"uid":34189,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"87ed77c60927bf2ffc385e466d4a2282d2a22e83","tid":984861,"uid":39381,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"用黃豆槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"用槍就唔叫掟啦"},{"pid":"d531f9d7e8e35d6a6b97e18788c1b9efd47b44f0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87ed77c60927bf2ffc385e466d4a2282d2a22e83","tid":984861,"uid":39381,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"用黃豆槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"最多都係氣槍既威力，仲弱過鋼珠子彈喎。"},{"pid":"15a7c37bd42cfcbc4feb26adaf75702a4b83f701","tid":984861,"uid":8776,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"掟入口，哽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7ec3aed5e40b08f65b29ae69ba094ff9144ba9","tid":984861,"uid":25758,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"彈指神通？"},{"pid":"cb9f25536690dc2669ffab3fd48d6163d7dc4852","tid":984861,"uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"黃藥師"},{"pid":"91f26194a8b1a9e9827801072f61e63e3d4a0d39","tid":984861,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"愛嚟掉嗰啲黃豆"},{"pid":"186692de3a2c3ded790bf0afc36bc7c6f0e673a7","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"15a7c37bd42cfcbc4feb26adaf75702a4b83f701","tid":984861,"uid":8776,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"掟入口，哽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"黃豆都哽得死，呢D人應該一早自然淘汰左啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3451c96fa21738f9f59eb574030eebd7843a286","tid":984861,"uid":190129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"北冥神功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c8dc040a591ac92c9bb0db773a45f522a7efe2","tid":984861,"uid":108022,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"68120d3479d093c21234310c8e9174c7c17ebd0d","tid":984861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcUL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7f2058c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&h=d8cfe54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月17日 <br />\n<br />\n婦涉向法官掟銀仔<br />\n女保安：一粒黃豆都可掟死人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190117/large/17la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190117%2Flarge%2F17la8p11.jpg&h=b708b6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女被告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】患抑鬱的醫管局前女工，自言不滿高院法官未有公平處理其民事索償案，涉向上訴庭三名法官「掟銀仔」洩憤，銀仔沒擊中任何人，但有女保安員報稱受驚。女工昨否認普通襲擊罪受審，強調當時「向冇人嘅地方掟，目的係唔想掟到人」；女保安則謂聽到「喀喀聲」即感生命有威脅，更反問女工：「一粒黃豆都可以掟死人，你有冇聽過？」案件下周三裁決。<br />\n<br />\n女被告賴容（50歲）沒律師代表，昨甫開庭即向裁判官香淑嫻訴說案發因由，堅稱只向無人的走廊擲幣，揚言「可以睇帶」。香官表示法庭只有錄音系統、並沒錄影功能，賴疑惑地問：「點解嘅？裝假狗呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒預計到有人如此大膽<br />\n<br />\n涉事女保安朱肖雲供稱，案發去年6月20日獲指派到4號法庭觀察被告舉動，坐在法官席前的她突然聽到「喀喀聲」，即望向聲音來源，發現有數個毫子硬幣。朱自言：「好詫異，點解會咁㗎？掟到我點算呢？」並稱當時「有驚」，沒預計到有人如此大膽，在莊嚴法庭內掟東西。香官問朱在哪一階段感害怕，她答：「睇到個銀仔時。」被告即謂：「你話你望到個銀仔開始驚，你望到個銀仔係一毫子，反而應該唔驚！」朱不同意，更反問：「一粒黃豆都可以掟死人，你有冇聽過？」被告面露詫異謂：「黃豆真係未聽過，嚇親我。」朱及後澄清聞聲已驚。<br />\n<br />\n高級保安員事後向上訴庭法官請示如何處理，法官只禁止被告再次入庭，未有下令報警，但副保安主任李興亞報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n被告稱只想投訴民事法官要求她索取醫療報告，後來她花費3.7萬元取得報告，法官卻指不呈交也可，「法官唔尊重法庭，叫市民點尊重？佢可以咁做，我哋市民都可以咁做。」案件表證成立，被告辯稱感萬般委屈，甚至打算自殺，當日原想找法官申冤，但投訴不果反遭保安包圍和監視，有感煩擾和嬲怒才擲硬幣，「我其實想去馬道立嗰度，但唔識去」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1527/18<br />\n■記者楊思雅  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n社交網「大量張學友飛」引黃牛黨現身　內地男遭南亞賊搶14萬元<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n司機涉危駕被捕　聖保羅校巴倒車撞死保母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"女被告賴容（50歲）沒律師代表，昨甫開庭即向裁判官香淑嫻訴說案發因由，堅稱只向無人的走廊擲幣，揚言「可以睇帶」。<span style=\"color: red;\">香官表示法庭只有錄音系統、並沒錄影功能</span>，賴疑惑地問：「點解嘅？裝假狗呀？」<br />\n<br />\n有律師有得打甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己上, 抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0353c12fead808c44363f464ca56c0dd39c806","tid":984861,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186692de3a2c3ded790bf0afc36bc7c6f0e673a7","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"15a7c37bd42cfcbc4feb26adaf75702a4b83f701","tid":984861,"uid":8776,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"6f61a485f20f3aadd7c01e46afdcb0a401247bb0","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"黃豆點樣掟死人？真心求教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"掟入口，哽死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"黃豆都哽得死，呢D人應該一早自然淘汰左啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"對黃豆敏感"},{"pid":"8d58c4b2b609a5899a016340782e72675be6e1d1","tid":984861,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57c8dc040a591ac92c9bb0db773a45f522a7efe2","tid":984861,"uid":108022,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"68120d3479d093c21234310c8e9174c7c17ebd0d","tid":984861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcUL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7f2058c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592844&h=d8cfe54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190117/20592844</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月17日 <br />\n<br />\n婦涉向法官掟銀仔<br />\n女保安：一粒黃豆都可掟死人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190117/large/17la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190117%2Flarge%2F17la8p11.jpg&h=b708b6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女被告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】患抑鬱的醫管局前女工，自言不滿高院法官未有公平處理其民事索償案，涉向上訴庭三名法官「掟銀仔」洩憤，銀仔沒擊中任何人，但有女保安員報稱受驚。女工昨否認普通襲擊罪受審，強調當時「向冇人嘅地方掟，目的係唔想掟到人」；女保安則謂聽到「喀喀聲」即感生命有威脅，更反問女工：「一粒黃豆都可以掟死人，你有冇聽過？」案件下周三裁決。<br />\n<br />\n女被告賴容（50歲）沒律師代表，昨甫開庭即向裁判官香淑嫻訴說案發因由，堅稱只向無人的走廊擲幣，揚言「可以睇帶」。香官表示法庭只有錄音系統、並沒錄影功能，賴疑惑地問：「點解嘅？裝假狗呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒預計到有人如此大膽<br />\n<br />\n涉事女保安朱肖雲供稱，案發去年6月20日獲指派到4號法庭觀察被告舉動，坐在法官席前的她突然聽到「喀喀聲」，即望向聲音來源，發現有數個毫子硬幣。朱自言：「好詫異，點解會咁㗎？掟到我點算呢？」並稱當時「有驚」，沒預計到有人如此大膽，在莊嚴法庭內掟東西。香官問朱在